data.slot:
Illuminate\View\ComponentSlot {#414
  +attributes: Illuminate\View\ComponentAttributeBag {#427
    #attributes: []
  }
  #contents: """
    <section class="homeparalax" style="background-image: url('pictures/DSCN4579.JPG')">\n
    \n
        </section>\n
    \n
        <section class="mx-96 my-10 flex flex-row justify-center"">\n
            <div class="text-left">\n
                <header100>\n
                    Convention videos\n
                </header100>\n
                <p>\n
                    We make videos here at ankerd about anime conventions in the Netherlands. We don't really make random\n
                    vlogs, just some goofy videos about conventions.\n
                </p>\n
                <p class="mt-4">\n
                    I simply enjoy the whole process of making a video, from filming to editing.\n
                    It's a creative outlet for me of some sorts. So please don't take it too seriously.\n
                </p>\n
            </div>\n
            <div style="width: 100%;" class="text-center">\n
                <iframe class="youtube2" width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2qfkxgsiCxQ" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n
                <div class="subscript">\n
                    Our favourite video so far\n
                </div>\n
            </div>\n
        </section>\n
        <!-- Ankerd Socials -->\n
        <section class="my-20 flex flex-row justify-center bg-black">\n
            <div class="my-5 flex flex-row">\n
                <a target="_blank" class="flex flex-col items-center px-5 no-underline" style="font-size: 100%;" class="link" href="https://www.youtube.com/@officialankerd"><i class="fa-brands fa-youtube fa-2xl p-4 text-white"></i>Youtube</a>\n
                <a target="_blank" class="flex flex-col items-center px-5 no-underline" style="font-size: 100%;" class="link" href="https://www.twitter.com/@officialankerd"><i class="fa-brands fa-twitter fa-2xl p-4 text-white"></i>Twitter</a>\n
                <a target="_blank" class="flex flex-col items-center px-5 no-underline" style="font-size: 100%;" class="link" href="https://www.instagram.com/ankerd_official/"><i class="fa-brands fa-instagram fa-2xl p-4 text-white"></i>Instagram</a>\n
            </div>\n
        </section>\n
        <!-- Gavin About -->\n
        <section class="mx-96 my-20 justify-center text-left">\n
            <div class="mb-10 mt-20 flex flex-row">\n
                <div class="w-1/3">\n
                    <image src="images/mandelbrot.png"></image>\n
                </div>\n
                <div class="w-2/3" style="margin-left: 15px;">\n
                    <header100>\n
                        About\n
                    </header100>\n
                    <p>\n
                        Ankerd was founded by gavin132_ back in December of 2021. I actually just wanted a proper domain name\n
                        so I could make websites However This website is still just one giant hobby project hosted and maintained by me,\n
                        which quickly grew to a pretty sizeable community. I don't really know what to do\n
                        with this website, for now I have my portfolio on here. I also have a few teeny tiny articles littered\n
                        across this site dating back to my high school days. Keep in mind that site will change a whole bunch\n
                        during it's development. This project will never be over.\n
                    </p>\n
                </div>\n
            </div>\n
            <hr class="hr2">\n
        </section>\n
        <!-- The Team -->\n
        <section class="justify center mx-96 my-10 flex flex-col gap-4 text-left">\n
            <div class="text-left">\n
                <header100>\n
                    The team\n
                </header100>\n
                <p>\n
                    We're basically a bunch of morons making videos at conventions. 99% of the people in our videos have\n
                    some kind of connection to the ankerd group.\n
                    The only place where you'll find strangers is in the photo collage at the end of every video.\n
                </p>\n
                <p class="mt-2">\n
                    If you ever come across one of us don't be afraid to say hi. (say hi with caution, pay attention to your\n
                    surroundings)\n
                    please don't take this nor us seriously.\n
                </p>\n
            </div>\n
            <div>\n
                <image alt="Picture of a few members of ankerd" aria-label="Picture of a few members of ankerd" class="imagehome" src="/images/DSC09108.JPG"></image>\n
            </div>\n
            <div class="text-center">\n
                <div class="subscript">\n
                    A few members of ankerd\n
                </div>\n
            </div>\n
        </section>\n
        <!-- Ankerd Channel content -->\n
        <section class="bluebox my-10 py-8">\n
            <div class="text-center">\n
                <header100>\n
                    official ankerd channel\n
                </header100>\n
                <p>You can find all of our convention videos here</p>\n
            </div>\n
            <div class="pb-2">\n
                <div class=" grid grid-cols-2 mx-96 items-center">\n
                    <iframe class="youtube2" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZiWUpSkJNaU?enablejsapi=1" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n
                    <iframe class="youtube2" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-cxHPnH4moI?enablejsapi=1" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n
                    <iframe class="youtube2" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2qfkxgsiCxQ?enablejsapi=1" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n
                    <iframe class="youtube2" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-cxHPnH4moI?enablejsapi=1" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n
                </div>\n
            </div>\n
        </section>\n
        <!-- Gavin Channel content -->\n
        <section class="my-10 flex flex-col justify-center">\n
            <div class="mt-10 text-center">\n
                <header100>gavin132's channel</header100>\n
            </div>\n
            <div class="my-10 flex flex-row justify-center gap-10">\n
                <iframe class="youtube" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-0duopd_FGk" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n
                <iframe class="youtube" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6-KIMfpeCEc" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n
            </div>\n
        </section>
    """
}
